<i>adverb</i>: 뻔지르르 [뻔지르르], 번지르르 [번지르르], 반지르르 [반지르르], 미끈미끈 [미끈미끈], 매끈히 [매끈히], 매끈매끈 [매끈매끈], 날렵히 [날ː려피] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뻔지르르 [뻔지르르]</dt><br>
<dd>1. greasily; slipperily; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>겉에 기름이나 물이 묻어서 윤이 나고 미끄러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being shiny and smooth as a result of oil or water on the surface.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deceptively; slickly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동 또는 사물 등이 실속 없이 겉으로만 그럴듯한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a remark, behavior, object, etc., just look good on the surface without substance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>번지르르 [번지르르]</dt><br>
<dd>1. greasily; slipperily; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>겉에 기름이나 물이 묻어서 윤이 나고 미끄러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being shiny and smooth due to oil or water on the surface.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deceptively; slickly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동 또는 사물 등이 실속 없이 겉으로만 그럴듯한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a remark, behavior, or object, etc., just looks good without substance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>반지르르 [반지르르]</dt><br>
<dd>1. greasily; slipperily; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>겉에 기름이나 물이 묻어서 윤이 나고 매끄러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being shiny and smooth due to oil or water on the surface.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deceptively; slickly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동 또는 사물 등이 실속 없이 겉으로만 그럴듯한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a remark, behavior, object, etc., just looks good without substance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>미끈미끈 [미끈미끈]</dt><br>
<dd>smoothly; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>울퉁불퉁하거나 거친 데가 없이 몹시 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being very soft without uneven or rough parts.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매끈히 [매끈히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>울퉁불퉁하거나 거친 데가 없이 미끄럽고 보드랍게.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a very smooth look without any bumpy or rough spot.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cleanly; nicely</dd><br>
<dd>겉모습이 훤하고 말끔하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an appearance that is clean and groomed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매끈매끈 [매끈매끈]</dt><br>
<dd>smoothly; sleekly</dd><br>
<dd>울퉁불퉁하거나 거친 데가 없이 아주 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a very smooth look without any bumpy or rough spot.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>날렵히 [날ː려피]</dt><br>
<dd>1. nimbly; quickly</dd><br>
<dd>가볍고 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an agile and quick manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sleekly; slenderly</dd><br>
<dd>모양이 아주 날씬해서 매끈하고 맵시가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very slim, sleek, and stylish shape.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>